msgid ""
"Create an ``AccountRestrictionTransaction``, with restrictionType "
"\"AllowAddress\".  Add to the array the modification created in the previous"
" step."
msgstr ""
"制限タイプ \"AllowAddress\" の ``AccountRestrictionTransaction`` "
"を作成してください。前の手順で作成した変更を配列に追加します。"

#: ../../source/guides/account/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:106
#: ../../source/guides/account/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:150
#: ../../source/guides/account/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:184
msgid "Sign and announce the transaction."
